text.section:
Regulations adopted under this subtitle may include:
Initial and continuing standards and procedures for accreditation, including education, training, examination, and job performance standards;
Standards and procedures for renewal of accreditation;
Standards and procedures for modification, suspension, or revocation of accreditation;
Different standards and procedures for different lead paint abatement services;
Standards and procedures for abatement involving the renovation, repair, and painting of lead-containing substances, including a requirement for lead-dust testing;
Recognition of accreditation or similar approvals of persons by other governmental entities; and
Such other provisions as may be necessary to effectuate the purposes of this subtitle.
